body:
Remembering hurts ll Prolouge

prolouge l 1 l 2 l 3 | 4 I 5 

Pairing: Tony Stark x reader

A/n: so this is the fic I posted recently about. I really hope you like it.

“Who are you?” a man with a black eyepatch asks “Y/n” I answer. “And do you have a last name” he continues. “No” I reply shortly. This man doesn’t need to know about my heritage.

I went to Midgard for one reason and one reason only; no more being the daughter of Odin. No. I hate that name. I won’t be that girl anymore. I hated my life. My father used me as a pawn in his game. He send me to kill my own sister. He hid the fact that I was the leader of the Valkery so I would look weak.

My regular y/c hair had to be blonde whenever in public, and my eyes blue. Even my own siblings didn’t know about my y/c hair and y/c eyes. No they have been fed a lie made by my father. They believe it.

I wish to know what lie my father told about my missing. He probably made some story about me being kidnapped and killed by the frostgiants.

“Do you remeber anything y/n?” the man questions. “No” I lie. “Well miss y/n welcome to Stragetic Homeland Intervention Enforcement and Logistic Division. Better known as SHIELD.” He shows me around a flying fortress. “We want to ask some questions”

body:
Superior Iron Man x Peter

∆ So Iron Man turns bad and sends out the Iron league to watch over everyone

∆ Tony Stark becomes the Mayor, Ruler, and Judge for New York all in one day

∆ A very controlling leader and is hungry for more power

∆ Then Peter Parker gets bitten by a radioactive spider

∆ Now Peter has looked up to Tony Stark all his life and immediately goes to him for help, because Tony can fix it right?

∆ Tony sees Peter as a threat and locks him up

∆ However once Hydra sends an attack at Stark base everything changes

∆ So now Tony takes the poor kid under his wing and trains him

∆ Peter is overjoyed, despite the fact that he spent months in a cold jail cell with hardly any food to survive on

∆ Tony starts to realise just how pretty his protege is

∆ After a celebration at ending Hydra’s Captain America, the two kiss

∆ Both drunk and high on lust the two stumble to bed

∆ Peter now wear a collar, ‘Tony’s Trophy’

∆ Tony lavishes Peter with gifts and such

∆ Once Aunt May finds out where Peter is she goes ballistic

∆ Unfortunately for her, Peter is already too fall into the Iron Man’s trap to realize that Tony had locked May up

∆ Fortunately for everyone, Tony is more of a kind leader thanks to Peter

∆ And pray for anyone who tries to harm the Superior leader’s trophy

body:
found myself in a difficult financial situation. it happend abruptly, but i’m not gonna talk about iti’m in need of my psychological therapy for what i have no finance.And i'am going to find a job but i want to  reserve  half a month i think, to do what i’m afraid i won’t have much time for= my art/ or be able doing like 1-2 per month( in a long time terms

that’s what i don’t want at all. in a short- i need a help to cover my expenses on my therapy

MY KO-FI

i don’t know how to organise art for what i will need much more time, please inform me if you are intrested even in commisioning me(if i were smarter i would open it)

because now  i offer u a sketchy art from me for 1 ko-fi or as u decide (use a ko-fi platform for this coffee commisions i guess?)

ALSO spam my askbox with art ideas you wanna see)0

Right now i need your ideas. You decide you wanna buy me  coffee for this or no

so if you are willing to support me like this i will be able to continue my therapy) if anyone would ever consider donatin i will be gratefull. it means so much to me<3

So it goes, 🙌love

Series: Part 1 of We’re Gonna Have to do This Together
Summary:

Being a superhero sometimes means you forget about the small dangers in the world, like disease. For Peter, this means he loses May to natural causes, not something he could ever save her from.

Unknown to him, May left custody of Peter in the hands of Tony Stark, who, even though he wants kids, has no idea how to actually raise one. With a grieving superhero teenager on his hands, Tony is going to have to figure it out quick, if he wants Peter to ever be able to move on and be happy.
